  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA59">
<l>paṇpuṇara māṭṭēṉṉā ṉīyē paṇittukkāṇ</l>
<l>kaṇpuṇaru neṟṟik kaṟaikkaṇṭā - peṇpuṇaru</l>
<l>mavvuruvō māluruvō vāṉēṟṟāy nīṟaṇiva</l>
<l>tevvuruvō niṉṉuruva mēl</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I cannot perceive [your] quality. You, direct [and] see,</l>
<l>you with a stained throat, the front joined by an eye. Is it that form</l>
<l>joined by a woman or is the form [joined by] Māl, you mounted on a bull?</l>
<l>Of your forms which is the form that is adorned with ashes?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
